            "descriptionRaw": "Unleashes a Celestial Dreamsphere that constantly fires Starlight Slugs at opponents within its AoE, dealing <color=#99FFFFFF>Cryo DMG</color>.\nWhen a Starlight Slug hits, it will generate 1 Night Star for nearby Curtains of Slumber. Each Curtain of Slumber can gain 1 Night Star this way every 0.5s.\n\n<i>\"Sleep now, sleep now; and may many destinies be revealed before your slumbering eyes, within your star-paved dreams.\"</i>",
            "name": "Dream of the Star-Stream Shaker"
        },
